Title: Expedition Effervesta
Description:
My daughter's gone missing--we have to find her!

As High Redolence, I may be the next target. $p, will you come with me?

I can still smell her, faintly. She has to still be in Loamm somewhere.

We have to hurry!
ObjectivesText: Search for clues about Effervesta's whereabouts in Zaralek Cavern.
